```python
class BaseTool(ABC):
    @property
    @abstractmethod
    def name(self) -> str: ...

    @property
    @abstractmethod
    def schema(self) -> dict: ...

    @abstractmethod
    async def execute(self, **params) -> ToolResult: ...
```

